FormatText.string: The Witch's Peat bar has been overrun, and people need their drinks to cope with life on Eden-6. Help Kay get the bar up and running.
Help Kay get her bar, The Witch's Peat, reopened. People are thirsty! You'll probably have to get your hands dirty and kill a few jabbers!
